course.subject: MATH
course.name: Reading Course: Regularity for Elliptic Equations of Second Order
course.description: De Giorgi-Nash-Moser theory for elliptic equations in divergence form, Krylov-Safonov theory for elliptic equations in non-divergence form, Schauder regularity theory, W^{2,p} regularity theory, viscosity solutions, fully nonlinear equations, Evans-Krylov theorem. Students should seek approval from the course instructor to take this course.
